Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

### Summary of the Alembic Workflow

Moving forward, every time you change a model (e.g., adding a username field to the User class):
* Modify your model in app/models.py.
* Generate a script: uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add username"
* Review the script in migrations/versions/.
* Apply to DB: uv run alembic upgrade head